  title: Table Notes
  pages:
  - 'Page 1


    This placeholder book is meant to be placed on tables, shelves,
    or counters.


    Interact with it to open the reader overlay.'
  - 'Page 2


    Use A / Left Arrow and D / Right Arrow to flip pages.


    Use
    E or Escape to close the overlay.'
  - 'Page 3


    Design note:

    Replace these serialized entries with clue text,
    tutorial notes, diary pages, or puzzle information.'
